high_descs: Turn around to reach the passage on the left and head into the bedroom on the left to reach the desk.
Pick up the pencil from the desk.
Turn around to reach the dresser.
Put the pencil in the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the pencil in the dresser.

high_descs: Turn right and turn left and again turn left move towards the desk.
Pick the pencil from the desk.
Turn left move towards the dresser.
Place the pencil inside the dresser.
anns.task_desc: To place  the pencil inside the dresser.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near desk.
Pick up pencil from the desk.
Turn around and walk to the dresser to your left.
anns.task_desc: Moving pencil from one place to another.
